EN: This river needs regular inspections to keep it clean.

ZH: 巡查人员必须保持警惕，以确保安全。
EN: Inspectors must remain vigilant to ensure safety.

ZH: 我们每月都会安排巡查，确保设备正常运行。
EN: We schedule monthly inspections to ensure equipment is running smoothly.

ZH: 巡查员会检查每个房间，确保没有问题。
EN: Inspectors will check every room to make sure there are no issues.

ZH: 巡查团队每周巡遍整个城市。
EN: The inspection team covers the entire city every week.

ZH: 巡查员得到了充分的培训，知道该如何应对紧急情况。
EN: Inspectors have received thorough training on how to deal with emergencies.

