EN: The inspection team conducts routine checks in the valleys to ensure the roads are clear.

ZH: 巡查人员负责检查建筑物是否符合建筑规范。
EN: Inspectors are responsible for checking if buildings comply with construction regulations.

ZH: 巡查部门已经采取了措施来加强食品安全。
EN: The inspection department has taken measures to enhance food safety.
